WEBVTT

00:00:00.006 --> 00:01:00.006

00:01:30.220 --> 00:01:32.980
[Episode 03]

00:01:36.150 --> 00:01:36.680
Auntie!

00:01:38.150 --> 00:01:38.590
Auntie!

00:01:39.680 --> 00:01:40.560
Can I see you off?

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:43.200
You're so tall now.

00:01:44.400 --> 00:01:45.790
You're still my auntie anyway.

00:01:46.350 --> 00:01:47.560
Weren't you working?

00:01:47.710 --> 00:01:48.710
Why did you come?

00:01:49.150 --> 00:01:50.120
Mom told me to.

00:01:50.840 --> 00:01:52.920
She's feeling much better.

00:01:53.230 --> 00:01:53.870
Seeing you

00:01:54.510 --> 00:01:55.510
really made her happy.

00:01:57.870 --> 00:01:58.640
Watch your step.

00:01:59.790 --> 00:02:00.590
It's a bit steep.

00:02:04.790 --> 00:02:05.350
Slow down.

00:02:07.790 --> 00:02:08.280
Here.

00:02:10.240 --> 00:02:11.080
This shortcut

00:02:11.240 --> 00:02:12.150
saves about 20 minutes.

00:02:12.590 --> 00:02:13.800
Or you'll be walking down

00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:14.630
in the dark

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:15.800
with no rides.

00:02:17.190 --> 00:02:17.680
Be careful.

00:02:23.870 --> 00:02:24.800
Still in school?

00:02:25.910 --> 00:02:26.520
Senior year.

00:02:27.630 --> 00:02:29.240
You're just a bit
younger than me, right?

00:02:29.630 --> 00:02:30.000
Yes.

00:02:30.710 --> 00:02:32.080
But due to my mom's illness,

00:02:32.710 --> 00:02:34.000
I took two leaves of absence.

00:02:34.280 --> 00:02:35.000
So I'm still a senior.

00:02:37.030 --> 00:02:37.840
How's school?

00:02:38.590 --> 00:02:39.120
Not bad.

00:02:39.430 --> 00:02:40.470
Our township high school

00:02:40.470 --> 00:02:41.590
is one of the top schools.

00:02:41.750 --> 00:02:43.280
I'm in the advanced class. Top five.

00:02:43.840 --> 00:02:45.360
Then college shouldn't be a problem.

00:02:48.120 --> 00:02:49.150
My family

00:02:49.710 --> 00:02:50.870
can't afford that.

00:02:52.310 --> 00:02:53.000
I wanna enlist.

00:02:53.590 --> 00:02:54.400
Then military academy.

00:02:55.400 --> 00:02:56.000
Remember?

00:02:56.190 --> 00:02:56.960
When I was little,

00:02:57.280 --> 00:02:59.280
I saw paratroopers and called them gods.

00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:02.280
It's not that I didn't get it.

00:03:02.710 --> 00:03:03.590
I've just always

00:03:03.710 --> 00:03:04.750
admired soldiers.

00:03:08.150 --> 00:03:08.710
Auntie,

00:03:09.870 --> 00:03:10.870
will you support me?

00:03:12.680 --> 00:03:13.430
Of course.

00:03:14.120 --> 00:03:15.400
If you get a chance,

00:03:15.680 --> 00:03:16.680
go for it.

00:03:19.310 --> 00:03:19.840
Auntie,

00:03:20.030 --> 00:03:20.870
please give

00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:22.310
my regards to Principal Fang.

00:03:23.190 --> 00:03:24.430
She's really kind.

00:03:24.680 --> 00:03:25.150
She came

00:03:25.150 --> 00:03:26.150
a few times.

00:03:26.560 --> 00:03:28.150
The clinic in our village

00:03:28.310 --> 00:03:29.560
was funded by her.

00:03:30.280 --> 00:03:31.000
She visited again?

00:03:31.960 --> 00:03:33.190
She didn't tell you?

00:03:36.000 --> 00:03:37.590
She deliberately didn't want me to know.

00:03:40.750 --> 00:03:42.710
My foster mother
passed away ten days ago.

00:03:44.590 --> 00:03:45.590
Before she died,

00:03:46.190 --> 00:03:47.280
she wrote me a letter.

00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:48.840
That's how I learned about my past

00:03:49.750 --> 00:03:51.190
and that I have

00:03:51.750 --> 00:03:52.960
some family...

00:04:04.680 --> 00:04:05.280
Give these

00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:06.870
to your grandpa,

00:04:07.030 --> 00:04:07.470
your mom,

00:04:07.590 --> 00:04:08.190
and my sister.

00:04:10.590 --> 00:04:12.000
Is this... money?

00:04:12.150 --> 00:04:13.870
Yeah, 1,000 yuan in each envelope.

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:14.630
No, Auntie.

00:04:14.870 --> 00:04:15.680
You don't have to.

00:04:16.270 --> 00:04:17.480
We're not well-off,

00:04:17.680 --> 00:04:18.920
but things are way better now.

00:04:19.310 --> 00:04:20.000
And every family

00:04:20.240 --> 00:04:21.360
has working hands.

00:04:21.560 --> 00:04:21.920
We can...

00:04:21.920 --> 00:04:23.310
Take the money.

00:04:23.830 --> 00:04:24.830
No more arguments.

00:04:27.430 --> 00:04:28.720
Alright, Auntie.

00:04:30.040 --> 00:04:30.600
But

00:04:31.430 --> 00:04:32.720
do you trust me?

00:04:33.600 --> 00:04:35.000
I trust anyone determined

00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:36.190
to join the army.

00:04:38.830 --> 00:04:39.360
I gotta go.

00:04:40.040 --> 00:04:40.600
Auntie,

00:04:40.920 --> 00:04:42.040
this honey is for you.

00:04:43.240 --> 00:04:43.720
Thanks.

00:04:56.160 --> 00:04:57.310
So much money!

00:05:00.160 --> 00:05:01.160
Help me

00:05:01.510 --> 00:05:02.510
count this.

00:05:03.390 --> 00:05:04.950
No need to count. It's 1,000 yuan.

00:05:05.510 --> 00:05:06.270
Auntie Wanzhi said it.

00:05:15.070 --> 00:05:16.390
Principal Fang

00:05:17.480 --> 00:05:18.800
shouldn't be so wasteful,

00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:20.360
though she's rich.

00:05:21.680 --> 00:05:23.390
That's no way to teach a child.

00:05:26.070 --> 00:05:28.070
She's got a life to live too.

00:05:28.870 --> 00:05:29.310
No!

00:05:30.390 --> 00:05:30.720
Mom!

00:05:30.750 --> 00:05:31.720
Can't take it!

00:05:31.720 --> 00:05:32.070
Mom!

00:05:33.070 --> 00:05:34.480
Give it back to her.

00:05:34.830 --> 00:05:36.510
She's already gone.

00:05:36.720 --> 00:05:38.480
How's he gonna catch her now?

00:05:38.950 --> 00:05:39.720
We'll return it

00:05:40.040 --> 00:05:41.270
but only when we're

00:05:41.270 --> 00:05:41.950
better off.

00:05:42.630 --> 00:05:43.310
Don't forget

00:05:43.360 --> 00:05:45.000
we're thousands in debt.

00:05:45.040 --> 00:05:45.800
Now we have this.

00:05:46.240 --> 00:05:47.240
We can pay off some.

00:05:47.600 --> 00:05:48.480
Let me catch a break,

00:05:48.800 --> 00:05:49.390
okay?

00:05:51.270 --> 00:05:52.000
(Come on! Cheers!)

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:52.720
(Have another!)

00:05:52.800 --> 00:05:53.800
(Let's enjoy!)

00:05:53.800 --> 00:05:54.800
- (Come on!)
- Dazhi!

00:05:56.560 --> 00:05:58.040
Zhao Dazhi!

00:05:58.680 --> 00:05:59.560
Hey,

00:06:00.040 --> 00:06:01.000
quit your yelling.

00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:03.720
Take a look

00:06:04.430 --> 00:06:05.750
at this.

00:06:07.390 --> 00:06:10.160
Never seen this much cash, have you?

00:06:10.480 --> 00:06:12.070
All new bills.

00:06:12.240 --> 00:06:12.750
Who gave this?

00:06:13.800 --> 00:06:14.720
My sister.

00:06:16.600 --> 00:06:18.360
You never thought

00:06:18.360 --> 00:06:19.800
we have such a rich relative, right?

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:20.600
My sister

00:06:20.920 --> 00:06:21.510
has a principal

00:06:21.920 --> 00:06:23.480
for a mom

00:06:23.720 --> 00:06:25.160
and a county head for a dad.

00:06:25.720 --> 00:06:26.430
That's

00:06:26.630 --> 00:06:28.920
some high-class family!

00:06:29.240 --> 00:06:30.120
When did you get a sister?

00:06:30.800 --> 00:06:32.040
I told you before.

00:06:32.480 --> 00:06:34.800
Same mom, same dad.

00:07:02.800 --> 00:07:03.390
Fang Wanzhi.

00:07:05.120 --> 00:07:06.360
You went to Shenxian Peak?

00:07:06.800 --> 00:07:08.040
Did you see Vice Mayor Meng?

00:07:09.120 --> 00:07:09.680
No.

00:07:10.950 --> 00:07:11.920
So my words

00:07:11.920 --> 00:07:13.040
meant nothing to you?

00:07:14.830 --> 00:07:15.830
No.

00:07:16.480 --> 00:07:17.240
He hasn't been home

00:07:17.240 --> 00:07:18.360
these days.

00:07:18.720 --> 00:07:19.360
I can't just

00:07:19.360 --> 00:07:20.240
go to his office.

00:07:20.240 --> 00:07:21.120
Why not?

00:07:21.430 --> 00:07:22.310
If you don't tell him

00:07:22.310 --> 00:07:23.560
and he finds out

00:07:23.630 --> 00:07:24.630
from someone else,

00:07:24.800 --> 00:07:25.680
you're done for!

00:07:27.040 --> 00:07:28.600
Why are you so angry?

00:07:29.160 --> 00:07:30.600
You have no respect

00:07:30.680 --> 00:07:31.750
for me.

00:07:32.360 --> 00:07:33.120
You can be stubborn

00:07:33.160 --> 00:07:34.360
and not tell me.

00:07:34.560 --> 00:07:35.160
But now

00:07:35.480 --> 00:07:36.480
you're making me

00:07:36.480 --> 00:07:37.160
lose face.

00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:40.750
Why do we need to save face between us?

00:07:41.160 --> 00:07:42.680
Lying is the real disrespect.

00:07:44.560 --> 00:07:45.120
Fine.

00:07:45.680 --> 00:07:46.560
I have to say,

00:07:47.480 --> 00:07:48.480
things are complicated now.

00:07:48.680 --> 00:07:49.920
Really complicated.

00:07:50.560 --> 00:07:51.480
You're a Fang.

00:07:51.560 --> 00:07:52.430
And you're growing apart

00:07:52.510 --> 00:07:53.240
from him.

00:07:53.360 --> 00:07:54.240
So you're losing

00:07:54.240 --> 00:07:55.360
the backing of a good family.

00:07:55.870 --> 00:07:57.240
When two people fall in love,

00:07:57.480 --> 00:07:58.160
their families

00:07:58.160 --> 00:07:59.240
get involved.

00:07:59.240 --> 00:08:00.240
Right?

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:01.360
Fang Wanzhi,

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:03.240
so much has changed.

00:08:03.600 --> 00:08:04.630
I think

00:08:04.720 --> 00:08:05.560
we need to cool off.

00:08:05.950 --> 00:08:07.000
Let's take a break.

00:08:28.630 --> 00:08:29.510
My first love...

00:08:32.270 --> 00:08:33.030
is over.

00:08:41.670 --> 00:08:42.870
Yudan, stop pouring.

00:08:42.870 --> 00:08:44.000
You think she hasn't had enough?

00:08:48.670 --> 00:08:49.240
Wanzhi,

00:08:50.200 --> 00:08:51.440
maybe there's still hope.

00:08:52.480 --> 00:08:54.270
After all, Han Bin didn't say it's over.

00:08:54.840 --> 00:08:56.080
Why not write him a letter?

00:08:56.600 --> 00:08:57.320
You write well.

00:08:57.390 --> 00:08:58.390
A letter

00:08:58.510 --> 00:08:59.870
might soften

00:08:59.960 --> 00:09:00.480
the blow.

00:09:00.960 --> 00:09:02.000
Write what?

00:09:02.600 --> 00:09:03.600
An apology?

00:09:03.840 --> 00:09:04.550
No way!

00:09:06.720 --> 00:09:08.120
There are plenty of fish in the sea.

00:09:08.270 --> 00:09:09.720
Plenty of good guys out there.

00:09:10.120 --> 00:09:10.720
Cheers!

00:09:10.790 --> 00:09:11.240
Cheers!

00:09:12.120 --> 00:09:12.910
Tough talk.

00:09:13.080 --> 00:09:13.960
You'll regret it soon.

00:09:14.240 --> 00:09:14.630
I...

00:09:16.240 --> 00:09:17.630
I already regret it.

00:09:20.120 --> 00:09:21.360
I've never dated before,

00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:23.360
but I thought

00:09:23.790 --> 00:09:24.840
I'd be the one

00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:26.600
to say bye first.

00:09:29.360 --> 00:09:31.120
Li Yudan, why are you laughing?

00:09:31.600 --> 00:09:32.200
Glad to see me

00:09:32.240 --> 00:09:33.240
get dumped?

00:09:33.720 --> 00:09:34.240
Yes!

00:09:34.510 --> 00:09:35.480
Yes? I...

00:09:36.120 --> 00:09:37.000
You brat!

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:50.630
What's for lunch?

00:09:51.000 --> 00:09:53.200
How about the cafeteria?

00:09:53.200 --> 00:09:54.000
It's pretty good.

00:09:54.360 --> 00:09:54.750
Sure.

00:09:55.720 --> 00:09:57.200
Let's play a good game today.

00:10:06.600 --> 00:10:07.270
(Wait!)

00:10:15.720 --> 00:10:16.240
Thanks.

00:10:26.240 --> 00:10:27.320
Such a busybody.

00:10:27.720 --> 00:10:28.720
Why did I press the button?

00:10:31.750 --> 00:10:32.870
Wanzhi, a letter for you.

00:10:41.550 --> 00:10:42.120
Not reading it?

00:10:42.960 --> 00:10:44.720
From Shenxian Peak. Not worth reading.

00:10:45.600 --> 00:10:46.630
Why did you go then?

00:10:48.960 --> 00:10:50.550
That's where my life began.

00:10:50.870 --> 00:10:52.240
If I hadn't seen it for myself,

00:10:52.360 --> 00:10:53.600
I'd feel like I let myself down.

00:10:54.120 --> 00:10:54.960
I'm done

00:10:54.960 --> 00:10:56.000
with Shenxian Peak.

00:10:56.670 --> 00:10:57.390
I'm at ease now.

00:10:58.080 --> 00:10:59.960
But it cost you.

00:11:00.240 --> 00:11:01.960
There goes your Prince Charming.

00:11:02.670 --> 00:11:03.750
Prince Charming?

00:11:03.960 --> 00:11:05.000
So cheesy.

00:11:05.750 --> 00:11:06.390
Other girls

00:11:06.550 --> 00:11:08.120
call Han Bin that.

00:11:09.030 --> 00:11:09.960
Soon every girl

00:11:10.030 --> 00:11:11.030
will be dating Han Bin.

00:11:11.270 --> 00:11:12.200
Don't miss it.

00:11:12.790 --> 00:11:13.550
What?

00:11:14.000 --> 00:11:16.240
Radio station, 8 PM.

00:11:16.870 --> 00:11:19.080
He'll recite "Saying Good-bye
to Cambridge Again"

00:11:19.240 --> 00:11:20.600
in Chinese and English.

00:11:20.960 --> 00:11:21.720
When word got out,

00:11:21.840 --> 00:11:23.440
the whole school went crazy.

00:11:26.080 --> 00:11:26.840
Boring.

00:11:41.360 --> 00:11:45.200
(Very quietly I take my leave)

00:11:46.270 --> 00:11:48.750
(As quietly as I came here;)

00:11:50.200 --> 00:11:52.200
(Quietly I wave good-bye)

00:11:53.000 --> 00:11:57.840
(To the rosy clouds in the western sky.)

00:11:59.480 --> 00:12:02.720
(Very quietly I take my leave)

00:12:03.960 --> 00:12:06.000
(As quietly as I came here;)

00:12:06.440 --> 00:12:09.080
(Quietly I wave good-bye)

00:12:10.150 --> 00:12:13.390
(To the rosy clouds in the western sky.)

00:12:13.550 --> 00:12:14.240
Wanzhi.

00:12:19.150 --> 00:12:20.270
Weren't you at the broadcast?

00:12:20.510 --> 00:12:21.390
It's pre-recorded.

00:12:28.790 --> 00:12:30.270
I just want a break.

00:12:30.600 --> 00:12:31.510
And you ignored me?

00:12:32.670 --> 00:12:33.670
The Princess of Yu County

00:12:33.670 --> 00:12:34.550
has quite the temper.

00:12:38.510 --> 00:12:40.240
They invited me several times.

00:12:40.510 --> 00:12:41.390
I always said no.

00:12:42.270 --> 00:12:43.030
Today,

00:12:43.390 --> 00:12:44.150
it was

00:12:44.240 --> 00:12:45.550
just for you, Fang Wanzhi.

00:12:47.030 --> 00:12:48.030
I knew

00:12:48.670 --> 00:12:49.670
you'd be here for me.

00:12:52.080 --> 00:12:53.440
Are you calm now?

00:12:54.270 --> 00:12:55.120
I admit

00:12:56.150 --> 00:12:57.000
I was impulsive.

00:12:58.000 --> 00:12:58.630
You know,

00:12:59.150 --> 00:13:00.360
if you break ties

00:13:00.390 --> 00:13:01.000
with Mr. Meng,

00:13:01.390 --> 00:13:02.790
then it'll be hard

00:13:02.870 --> 00:13:04.270
to convince my parents to accept us.

00:13:05.440 --> 00:13:06.390
But no matter how hard,

00:13:07.150 --> 00:13:07.630
I still want

00:13:07.670 --> 00:13:08.910
to be with you.

00:13:33.360 --> 00:13:35.030
Of course he came back to me.

00:13:35.390 --> 00:13:36.240
Apologizing

00:13:36.270 --> 00:13:37.270
is not my thing.

00:13:37.840 --> 00:13:39.390
What spirit.

00:13:43.510 --> 00:13:44.150
Fang Wanzhi.

00:13:44.630 --> 00:13:45.910
Your relatives are waiting.

00:13:46.510 --> 00:13:47.150
My relatives?

00:13:48.510 --> 00:13:49.030
Over there.

00:13:53.750 --> 00:13:54.360
Hello?

00:13:57.670 --> 00:13:58.150
Wanzhi,

00:13:58.750 --> 00:13:59.630
I'm Zhao Dazhi,

00:14:00.390 --> 00:14:01.480
your brother-in-law.

00:14:05.510 --> 00:14:06.150
Wanzhi,

00:14:06.270 --> 00:14:07.120
come here.

00:14:10.600 --> 00:14:11.480
Let me introduce them.

00:14:12.030 --> 00:14:12.870
This is the village chief.

00:14:13.120 --> 00:14:13.670
Also a Zhao.

00:14:14.550 --> 00:14:15.790
Zhao Kai's eldest uncle.

00:14:16.270 --> 00:14:17.270
Zhao Kai's third uncle.

00:14:17.630 --> 00:14:18.270
A militia captain.

00:14:18.390 --> 00:14:19.150
Also a cadre.

00:14:21.320 --> 00:14:21.960
Hi.

00:14:26.510 --> 00:14:27.150
Wanzhi,

00:14:27.670 --> 00:14:28.630
new sweet potatoes.

00:14:29.000 --> 00:14:30.200
For Vice Mayor Meng.

00:14:31.550 --> 00:14:32.630
And here are some eggs.

00:14:33.270 --> 00:14:33.960
Don't mind the size.

00:14:34.150 --> 00:14:35.270
Our village is up high,

00:14:35.510 --> 00:14:36.720
so they're small,

00:14:36.840 --> 00:14:37.630
but tasty.

00:14:37.720 --> 00:14:38.320
Right.

00:14:42.150 --> 00:14:43.750
You haven't eaten yet, have you?

00:14:45.510 --> 00:14:46.240
Enjoy yourselves.

00:14:47.510 --> 00:14:47.960
This...

00:14:48.120 --> 00:14:49.510
this is so generous.

00:14:50.240 --> 00:14:51.870
Thanks for your kindness.

00:14:57.360 --> 00:14:59.080
Actually, we came

00:14:59.630 --> 00:15:00.750
because we needed your help.

00:15:01.320 --> 00:15:02.480
I know you have a daughter.

00:15:02.630 --> 00:15:03.600
She's looking for a job.

00:15:04.000 --> 00:15:05.120
But I can't help with that.

00:15:05.360 --> 00:15:05.840
No.

00:15:06.440 --> 00:15:07.120
I wouldn't be

00:15:07.240 --> 00:15:08.120
that selfish.

00:15:08.670 --> 00:15:10.440
You're our only high-class relative.

00:15:10.510 --> 00:15:11.750
Only for the village

00:15:11.910 --> 00:15:13.510
would I have the guts to come.

00:15:14.080 --> 00:15:15.840
Yeah, it's for our village.

00:15:16.840 --> 00:15:18.270
You're not from Shenxian Peak?

00:15:18.600 --> 00:15:19.080
We...

00:15:20.600 --> 00:15:21.670
My bad. I didn't explain.

00:15:22.120 --> 00:15:24.000
They're from my village.

00:15:24.120 --> 00:15:25.200
Fifteen kilometers away.

00:15:25.440 --> 00:15:25.910
Yes.

00:15:26.000 --> 00:15:27.360
But why come to me

00:15:27.360 --> 00:15:28.510
about your village?

00:15:29.630 --> 00:15:31.480
Your dad's the vice mayor.

00:15:32.120 --> 00:15:33.960
But we can't just

00:15:33.960 --> 00:15:34.840
see him anytime.

00:15:35.480 --> 00:15:38.320
You're easier to reach than him.

00:15:38.840 --> 00:15:39.480
But...

00:15:39.960 --> 00:15:40.840
Ten years ago,

00:15:41.080 --> 00:15:42.320
because of you,

00:15:42.720 --> 00:15:44.240
Principal Fang started paying attention

00:15:44.240 --> 00:15:45.200
to Shenxian Peak.

00:15:45.870 --> 00:15:46.750
She built a clinic

00:15:47.080 --> 00:15:48.840
and sent a few doctors there.

00:15:49.440 --> 00:15:51.200
It helped a ton.

00:15:51.840 --> 00:15:53.000
But our village has nothing.

00:15:53.750 --> 00:15:54.240
Well,

00:15:54.720 --> 00:15:55.360
last month,

00:15:56.000 --> 00:15:57.840
when Sui's daughter-in-law
went into labor,

00:15:58.480 --> 00:15:59.360
heavy rain

00:15:59.720 --> 00:16:01.510
flooded the road to the town.

00:16:02.080 --> 00:16:02.720
And she had

00:16:04.120 --> 00:16:05.080
a difficult labor.

00:16:05.840 --> 00:16:06.360
In the end...

00:16:08.120 --> 00:16:09.360
she and her kid died.

00:16:11.030 --> 00:16:11.840
We made

00:16:12.120 --> 00:16:13.080
some inquiries.

00:16:13.600 --> 00:16:15.120
The county has funds

00:16:15.120 --> 00:16:16.720
for village clinics.

00:16:17.200 --> 00:16:17.840
However,

00:16:18.240 --> 00:16:19.440
our village is remote,

00:16:19.750 --> 00:16:20.720
and we have no connections.

00:16:21.080 --> 00:16:21.600
Hence,

00:16:22.120 --> 00:16:23.600
we came to ask you for help.

00:16:23.870 --> 00:16:24.240
Yeah.

00:16:24.360 --> 00:16:24.840
Right.

00:16:30.240 --> 00:16:30.840
Mr. Xiao,

00:16:31.120 --> 00:16:32.080
that's the situation.

00:16:32.720 --> 00:16:34.440
Can you help out?

00:16:36.720 --> 00:16:37.320
Okay.

00:16:37.670 --> 00:16:38.910
I'll have them come see you.

00:16:40.480 --> 00:16:41.000
Thank you.

00:16:50.960 --> 00:16:52.630
Go to Jianglin and find Director Xiao.

00:16:52.720 --> 00:16:53.440
He agreed to help.

00:16:55.670 --> 00:16:56.790
I can't take these.

00:16:57.000 --> 00:16:57.720
I have class.

00:16:57.870 --> 00:16:58.320
Bye.

00:16:58.790 --> 00:16:59.320
But... you...

00:16:59.720 --> 00:17:00.510
Wanzhi, you...

00:17:04.720 --> 00:17:05.480
Doing laundry?

00:17:05.640 --> 00:17:06.000
Yeah.

00:17:08.720 --> 00:17:09.240
Wanzhi,

00:17:09.440 --> 00:17:10.270
another letter.

00:17:14.400 --> 00:17:15.480
Not from Shenxian Peak.

00:17:15.680 --> 00:17:16.590
Another village.

00:17:16.720 --> 00:17:17.640
From their committee.

00:17:36.480 --> 00:17:38.160
These officials really
know how to flatter.

00:17:38.480 --> 00:17:39.030
They made you

00:17:39.070 --> 00:17:39.920
sound like a saint.

00:17:41.160 --> 00:17:42.510
Their village is struggling.

00:17:43.480 --> 00:17:45.310
I did a good thing.

00:17:46.030 --> 00:17:46.480
Wait.

00:17:47.160 --> 00:17:48.160
Go call

00:17:48.160 --> 00:17:48.880
Mr. Meng.

00:17:49.680 --> 00:17:50.240
Why?

00:17:50.510 --> 00:17:51.510
To thank him.

00:17:51.920 --> 00:17:52.680
You took

00:17:52.680 --> 00:17:53.240
this errand.

00:17:53.400 --> 00:17:54.720
It's not some errand.

00:17:56.270 --> 00:17:57.640
I didn't go to him either.

00:17:58.200 --> 00:17:59.200
Come on!

00:17:59.240 --> 00:18:00.480
Mr. Xiao wouldn't dare do you a favor

00:18:00.480 --> 00:18:01.480
without his boss's approval.

00:18:03.400 --> 00:18:04.480
Forget the call.

00:18:05.000 --> 00:18:05.960
Go to Yu County.

00:18:06.070 --> 00:18:07.480
Thank him in person and apologize.

00:18:07.880 --> 00:18:09.030
Plus, mend fences.

00:18:11.310 --> 00:18:12.720
That's way too deliberate.

00:18:14.000 --> 00:18:15.680
My mom's 35th-day
memorial is in a few days.

00:18:16.000 --> 00:18:16.750
Then...

00:18:16.750 --> 00:18:18.480
That's a perfect opportunity.

00:18:18.720 --> 00:18:19.640
Apologize to Mr. Meng

00:18:19.750 --> 00:18:21.110
at Principal Fang's grave.

00:18:21.310 --> 00:18:22.310
Way more effective.

00:18:23.960 --> 00:18:25.000
That sounds

00:18:25.030 --> 00:18:26.240
so wrong.

00:18:30.160 --> 00:18:31.590
I'm just trying to help you.

00:18:31.680 --> 00:18:33.160
Had to make it sound official.

00:18:45.880 --> 00:18:46.680
What's

00:18:46.720 --> 00:18:47.270
with the luggage?

00:18:48.400 --> 00:18:49.680
I'll go to Yu County with my sister.

00:18:49.680 --> 00:18:50.070
Hold on.

00:18:53.440 --> 00:18:54.720
A train ticket?

00:18:55.880 --> 00:18:56.640
Hard seat.

00:18:56.960 --> 00:18:57.960
A ten-hour slow train.

00:18:58.000 --> 00:18:59.000
Wanna wear her out?

00:19:02.310 --> 00:19:03.070
We talked it over.

00:19:03.680 --> 00:19:04.400
Tomorrow morning,

00:19:05.070 --> 00:19:06.070
I'm taking her back.

00:19:07.590 --> 00:19:09.920
Wanzhi's going back for family matters.

00:19:10.350 --> 00:19:11.240
It's only natural

00:19:11.310 --> 00:19:12.030
I go with her.

00:19:12.510 --> 00:19:13.590
Outsiders shouldn't

00:19:13.750 --> 00:19:14.830
get involved.

00:19:17.480 --> 00:19:18.400
Wanzhi told me

00:19:18.510 --> 00:19:19.310
how you two met.

00:19:19.590 --> 00:19:21.110
It's hard for a poor student like you

00:19:21.270 --> 00:19:22.590
to get into

00:19:22.750 --> 00:19:23.640
such a good university.

00:19:26.070 --> 00:19:27.790
You're playing the little brother

00:19:28.110 --> 00:19:29.070
to get a job

00:19:29.240 --> 00:19:30.070
from Mr. Meng, right?

00:19:31.070 --> 00:19:32.000
Pretty forward-thinking.

00:19:32.590 --> 00:19:33.110
It's fine

00:19:33.110 --> 00:19:34.270
if Mr. Meng won't help.

00:19:34.960 --> 00:19:36.240
I'd be happy to help you.

00:19:39.920 --> 00:19:41.750
But you're just a fishmonger's son

00:19:42.480 --> 00:19:43.550
and calling Wanzhi your sister.

00:19:43.830 --> 00:19:45.590
Don't you know it hurts

00:19:45.880 --> 00:19:46.880
Mr. Meng's reputation?

00:19:51.070 --> 00:19:52.480
Not once did she say that.

00:20:03.110 --> 00:20:03.790
Han Bin?

00:20:04.590 --> 00:20:05.510
Why are you here?

00:20:06.590 --> 00:20:08.310
I guessed you'd come
to the train station.

00:20:09.590 --> 00:20:10.640
You're here to see me off?

00:20:11.160 --> 00:20:12.030
Not exactly.

00:20:12.240 --> 00:20:13.110
I'm here to take you

00:20:13.110 --> 00:20:14.110
to my brother's party.

00:20:14.510 --> 00:20:15.310
A classy party.

00:20:15.480 --> 00:20:17.070
Invited guests are all high-level.

00:20:17.550 --> 00:20:18.310
I don't have time

00:20:18.400 --> 00:20:19.510
for some party.

00:20:19.830 --> 00:20:20.920
My brother is on his way.

00:20:21.000 --> 00:20:22.000
Our train's tonight.

00:20:22.160 --> 00:20:23.590
Didn't I tell you yesterday?

00:20:24.240 --> 00:20:25.590
I ran into Li Xingke

00:20:26.590 --> 00:20:27.790
and had him cancel the tickets.

00:20:28.030 --> 00:20:28.590
Cancel?

00:20:30.350 --> 00:20:32.070
I'm going with you to Yu County.

00:20:32.350 --> 00:20:33.030
Don't need him.

00:20:33.680 --> 00:20:35.640
He wasn't willing anyway.

00:20:36.400 --> 00:20:37.550
He wasn't willing?

00:20:38.790 --> 00:20:39.550
You know what?

00:20:40.000 --> 00:20:41.350
Visiting graves brings bad luck.

00:20:41.750 --> 00:20:42.510
Poor families

00:20:42.590 --> 00:20:43.590
care about that stuff.

00:20:46.270 --> 00:20:47.550
Don't ask him.

00:20:48.030 --> 00:20:48.920
He didn't say anything,

00:20:49.070 --> 00:20:49.920
but I could tell.

00:20:50.310 --> 00:20:51.510
I'm good on my own.

00:20:52.070 --> 00:20:52.790
I will

00:20:52.920 --> 00:20:53.590
talk to my dad

00:20:53.680 --> 00:20:55.310
and be clear about us.

00:20:55.680 --> 00:20:56.590
Then you two can meet.

00:20:56.830 --> 00:20:57.680
No way.

00:20:57.920 --> 00:20:59.000
I've already prepared a gift

00:20:59.000 --> 00:20:59.680
for him.

00:21:06.270 --> 00:21:07.160
Cigarettes and liquor

00:21:07.310 --> 00:21:08.160
are too tacky

00:21:08.270 --> 00:21:09.110
for Mr. Meng.

00:21:09.510 --> 00:21:10.310
This is the latest

00:21:10.400 --> 00:21:11.480
collector's edition.

00:21:11.640 --> 00:21:12.720
Only 1,000 sets nationwide.

00:21:13.510 --> 00:21:14.270
That's

00:21:14.310 --> 00:21:15.350
a thoughtful gift.

00:21:16.790 --> 00:21:18.270
The train's exhausting and filthy.

00:21:18.350 --> 00:21:19.510
And over ten hours.

00:21:20.880 --> 00:21:21.590
That's torture.

00:21:22.310 --> 00:21:22.590
So

00:21:22.830 --> 00:21:23.830
let's hit the party

00:21:24.310 --> 00:21:24.830
and feast.

00:21:25.030 --> 00:21:26.110
We'll leave at 5 AM tomorrow

00:21:26.240 --> 00:21:27.070
and arrive by nine.

00:21:27.310 --> 00:21:28.070
Nothing will be held up.

00:21:30.160 --> 00:21:30.590
Come on.

00:21:31.480 --> 00:21:31.880
Please.

00:21:48.640 --> 00:21:50.160
What a gorgeous house!
(Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org)

00:21:56.920 --> 00:21:58.400
Not taking this now.

00:21:58.680 --> 00:21:59.640
It'd be too awkward.

00:21:59.680 --> 00:22:00.790
My dad won't accept it.

00:22:01.070 --> 00:22:02.000
Next time I come,

00:22:02.070 --> 00:22:02.920
I may not have a car.

00:22:03.110 --> 00:22:04.640
Carrying this on the train is tiring.

00:22:05.200 --> 00:22:05.720
Just keep it

00:22:06.110 --> 00:22:06.880
at your home.

00:22:07.400 --> 00:22:08.310
When we get married,

00:22:09.000 --> 00:22:09.830
I'll give it

00:22:10.200 --> 00:22:11.310
to my father-in-law.

00:22:11.550 --> 00:22:12.160
Okay?

00:22:14.160 --> 00:22:14.640
Fine.

00:22:19.160 --> 00:22:20.110
I'll wait for your call.

00:22:20.960 --> 00:22:21.550
Bye.

00:22:26.920 --> 00:22:27.480
Wanzhi?

00:22:27.960 --> 00:22:28.550
Grandma Yu!

00:22:28.920 --> 00:22:29.680
I'm home.

00:22:30.310 --> 00:22:30.920
Welcome back.

00:22:31.240 --> 00:22:32.160
I missed you so much.

00:22:32.310 --> 00:22:33.550
I missed you too.

00:22:34.920 --> 00:22:35.550
Where's Dad?

00:22:36.440 --> 00:22:37.590
In the study.

00:22:38.590 --> 00:22:39.590
Gotta put my bags down.

00:23:04.350 --> 00:23:04.880
Dad.

00:23:06.550 --> 00:23:07.160
You're back!

00:23:08.350 --> 00:23:08.830
Good.

00:23:10.310 --> 00:23:11.350
Guoqing heard

00:23:11.440 --> 00:23:12.590
you'd come back today

00:23:13.160 --> 00:23:14.680
and wanted to pick you up.

00:23:15.510 --> 00:23:16.920
I told him not to.

00:23:19.790 --> 00:23:21.400
Let's just walk together

00:23:22.070 --> 00:23:22.830
to see your mom.

00:23:36.310 --> 00:23:38.070
Your hair's gotten grayer.

00:23:39.350 --> 00:23:40.350
I'm getting old.

00:23:41.400 --> 00:23:42.400
It's natural.

00:23:43.440 --> 00:23:44.000
No big deal.

00:23:48.880 --> 00:23:49.310
Dad,

00:23:50.640 --> 00:23:52.440
I have a lot to say to you.

00:23:53.200 --> 00:23:54.920
So do I.

00:23:55.960 --> 00:23:56.640
No rush.

00:23:57.240 --> 00:23:58.440
At your mom's grave,

00:23:58.830 --> 00:23:59.920
we will

00:23:59.920 --> 00:24:00.640
say it all.

00:24:28.110 --> 00:24:28.680
Mom,

00:24:29.440 --> 00:24:30.590
we're here to see you.

00:24:31.310 --> 00:24:33.160
I made Dad angry before.

00:24:33.920 --> 00:24:34.880
That was my fault.

00:24:35.720 --> 00:24:36.590
It won't happen again.

00:24:43.000 --> 00:24:43.720
Jingyu,

00:24:44.440 --> 00:24:45.830
after you left us,

00:24:46.110 --> 00:24:47.160
we were both

00:24:47.240 --> 00:24:48.070
in a bad place.

00:24:49.270 --> 00:24:50.240
So my attitude

00:24:50.270 --> 00:24:51.070
was off.

00:24:51.440 --> 00:24:52.880
Today, in front of you,

00:24:53.720 --> 00:24:55.160
I want to apologize to her.

00:24:56.640 --> 00:24:57.240
I'm sorry.

00:25:01.070 --> 00:25:01.830
It's behind us now.

00:25:02.240 --> 00:25:03.550
Speak your mind.

00:25:04.400 --> 00:25:05.200
You first.

00:25:06.400 --> 00:25:07.160
Fine.

00:25:07.830 --> 00:25:09.310
Lately,

00:25:10.160 --> 00:25:11.550
villagers from Shenxian Peak

00:25:12.160 --> 00:25:13.550
have used my name

00:25:14.750 --> 00:25:16.590
to get into offices in Jianglin City

00:25:16.590 --> 00:25:18.110
and ask for favors.

00:25:18.640 --> 00:25:19.240
Four times.

00:25:19.880 --> 00:25:20.830
Four times!

00:25:20.920 --> 00:25:21.350
Yes.

00:25:22.110 --> 00:25:23.830
Even more at the Yu County government.

00:25:24.240 --> 00:25:25.790
Two or three groups show up every week,

00:25:26.160 --> 00:25:27.200
claiming to be

00:25:27.200 --> 00:25:28.110
my relatives

00:25:28.720 --> 00:25:29.720
and demanding

00:25:30.160 --> 00:25:31.830
special treatment.

00:25:32.240 --> 00:25:32.790
I...

00:25:34.400 --> 00:25:35.750
How could they do that?

00:25:36.640 --> 00:25:38.000
They came to me once.

00:25:38.160 --> 00:25:39.400
And I asked Mr. Xiao for help.

00:25:40.000 --> 00:25:41.920
But just that once.

00:25:42.440 --> 00:25:43.160
He told me

00:25:43.160 --> 00:25:44.310
about that.

00:25:44.960 --> 00:25:47.000
I approved it years ago
when I was county head.

00:25:47.310 --> 00:25:48.400
But it never got done right.

00:25:48.880 --> 00:25:50.480
I was guilty about it.

00:25:51.830 --> 00:25:52.680
I didn't know

00:25:52.830 --> 00:25:54.000
it would cause you trouble.

00:25:54.400 --> 00:25:55.310
Not really.

00:25:56.000 --> 00:25:57.400
But the way they did it

00:25:57.720 --> 00:25:58.590
caught me off guard.

00:25:59.400 --> 00:26:00.480
You should tell them

00:26:01.510 --> 00:26:02.200
it's better

00:26:02.200 --> 00:26:03.680
to go through

00:26:04.310 --> 00:26:04.880
official ways

00:26:05.880 --> 00:26:07.590
like the township government

00:26:08.000 --> 00:26:08.830
or complaints office.

00:26:11.350 --> 00:26:12.350
Han Bin was right.

00:26:13.640 --> 00:26:14.790
He told me

00:26:14.880 --> 00:26:16.070
not to go to Shenxian Peak.

00:26:16.680 --> 00:26:17.680
I didn't listen.

00:26:18.920 --> 00:26:20.310
Sorry, Dad.

00:26:20.960 --> 00:26:21.920
I didn't go

00:26:22.030 --> 00:26:23.160
to find family.

00:26:24.160 --> 00:26:25.920
I just wanted to see it for myself.

00:26:26.720 --> 00:26:27.550
I understand.

00:26:28.480 --> 00:26:29.960
By the way, Han Bin...

00:26:30.640 --> 00:26:31.480
You two...

00:26:32.880 --> 00:26:34.440
We broke up before.

00:26:34.590 --> 00:26:35.680
But we got back together.

00:26:37.070 --> 00:26:38.200
He's a good guy.

00:26:38.440 --> 00:26:39.240
He's

00:26:39.350 --> 00:26:40.310
on the student council.

00:26:40.510 --> 00:26:41.750
Really cultured

00:26:41.920 --> 00:26:43.070
and organized.

00:26:43.480 --> 00:26:44.640
His take on things

00:26:44.830 --> 00:26:45.830
shows maturity.

00:26:47.200 --> 00:26:47.640
Besides,

00:26:48.110 --> 00:26:49.790
he kept pushing me to come back

00:26:49.920 --> 00:26:50.880
and apologize to you.

00:26:51.480 --> 00:26:52.550
He even rented a car

00:26:52.550 --> 00:26:53.400
to bring me back.

00:26:54.110 --> 00:26:54.480
Then...

00:26:54.920 --> 00:26:56.110
why didn't I see him?

00:26:56.640 --> 00:26:58.110
There was that misunderstanding.

00:26:58.240 --> 00:26:59.680
So he didn't wanna come uninvited.

00:27:00.310 --> 00:27:01.070
Said it'd be rude.

00:27:02.000 --> 00:27:03.160
He wants to take you out

00:27:03.350 --> 00:27:03.920
for a meal.

00:27:04.590 --> 00:27:05.480
If you mind it,

00:27:05.590 --> 00:27:06.590
we can pick up the tab.

00:27:07.640 --> 00:27:08.960
Since he's dating you

00:27:09.830 --> 00:27:10.830
and came here,

00:27:11.400 --> 00:27:12.790
he should come eat at home with us.

00:27:14.960 --> 00:27:15.720
But he thinks

00:27:15.830 --> 00:27:17.240
Grandma Yu is too old

00:27:17.400 --> 00:27:18.350
to have guests.

00:27:18.920 --> 00:27:19.920
Sounds like

00:27:20.480 --> 00:27:22.000
he's a nice man.

00:27:24.200 --> 00:27:25.640
Maybe I misjudged him.

00:27:28.680 --> 00:27:29.640
Why not go over?

00:27:31.200 --> 00:27:31.590
We...

00:27:32.160 --> 00:27:33.000
shouldn't we all

00:27:33.000 --> 00:27:33.920
pay respects together?

00:27:34.350 --> 00:27:35.400
They didn't bring

00:27:35.790 --> 00:27:36.880
any offerings.

00:27:37.310 --> 00:27:38.640
I've got the dessert

00:27:38.720 --> 00:27:39.920
Principal Fang loved.

00:27:40.000 --> 00:27:40.480
Mom,

00:27:42.200 --> 00:27:42.920
maybe...

00:27:43.960 --> 00:27:45.480
Mr. Meng and Fang Wanzhi

00:27:45.480 --> 00:27:46.310
want some privacy.

00:27:47.350 --> 00:27:47.920
We should wait

00:27:47.920 --> 00:27:49.000
until they leave.

00:27:50.790 --> 00:27:52.200
What's with the full name?

00:27:53.550 --> 00:27:54.350
What's wrong?

00:27:54.720 --> 00:27:55.720
Mom, just drop it.

00:28:04.160 --> 00:28:05.000
Where's Mr. Meng?

00:28:06.350 --> 00:28:07.350
He's delayed.

00:28:07.440 --> 00:28:08.200
We eat first.

00:28:09.160 --> 00:28:09.880
He agreed to come?

00:28:10.200 --> 00:28:10.880
Wonderful!

00:28:11.070 --> 00:28:11.680
Sit down.

00:28:15.310 --> 00:28:16.480
Doesn't matter how long.

00:28:16.480 --> 00:28:17.960
We'll wait.

00:28:22.550 --> 00:28:23.400
How was your talk

00:28:23.550 --> 00:28:24.200
with Mr. Meng?

00:28:24.590 --> 00:28:25.480
All good now?

00:28:26.880 --> 00:28:27.790
It wasn't a big deal.

00:28:28.000 --> 00:28:29.070
All good once we talked.

00:28:29.350 --> 00:28:30.590
I knew it.

00:28:30.880 --> 00:28:31.720
He even took care of

00:28:31.880 --> 00:28:32.550
a minor matter

00:28:32.680 --> 00:28:34.070
like a village clinic.

00:28:34.400 --> 00:28:35.070
That shows

00:28:35.160 --> 00:28:35.920
how close you two are.

00:28:36.550 --> 00:28:37.000
Wanzhi,

00:28:37.400 --> 00:28:38.440
don't do something

00:28:38.550 --> 00:28:39.400
that foolish again.

00:28:39.640 --> 00:28:40.590
It's a waste.

00:28:42.480 --> 00:28:42.920
Got it.

00:28:45.830 --> 00:28:47.070
Today's a good chance.

00:28:47.550 --> 00:28:48.880
We need to plan this right.

00:28:49.350 --> 00:28:50.160
For your future,

00:28:50.440 --> 00:28:50.880
of course,

00:28:51.160 --> 00:28:51.790
and for

00:28:51.790 --> 00:28:52.640
our future.

00:28:52.960 --> 00:28:53.640
We're a team.

00:28:54.960 --> 00:28:56.720
Looks like you have an idea.

00:29:00.720 --> 00:29:01.920
Mr. Meng

00:29:02.000 --> 00:29:03.160
is a great leader.

00:29:03.480 --> 00:29:04.400
The project is huge,

00:29:04.590 --> 00:29:05.960
and there are so many contracts.

00:29:06.200 --> 00:29:07.110
If he supports

00:29:07.160 --> 00:29:07.880
my brother's firm,

00:29:08.000 --> 00:29:08.720
then... you know.

00:29:10.310 --> 00:29:10.960
My brother

00:29:11.310 --> 00:29:13.160
promised to go halves on the profit.

00:29:14.480 --> 00:29:15.640
You think that's a good idea?

00:29:15.920 --> 00:29:17.030
Why wouldn't it be?

00:29:17.110 --> 00:29:18.160
When we get married,

00:29:18.160 --> 00:29:19.200
we'll need a three-bedroom.

00:29:19.200 --> 00:29:19.790
And kids mean

00:29:19.790 --> 00:29:21.070
at least two apartments.

00:29:21.160 --> 00:29:21.680
He says

00:29:21.920 --> 00:29:22.960
this one deal will get us

00:29:23.000 --> 00:29:24.110
the best house in the city.

00:29:24.400 --> 00:29:25.110
Stop dreaming!

00:29:29.110 --> 00:29:29.550
Wanzhi!

00:29:30.110 --> 00:29:30.640
Wanzhi!

00:29:34.510 --> 00:29:35.480
There's something

00:29:36.400 --> 00:29:37.400
I should tell you.

00:29:37.920 --> 00:29:39.160
Director Han's eldest son

00:29:39.400 --> 00:29:40.070
is Han Shuang.

00:29:40.960 --> 00:29:42.240
He's also Han Bin's brother.

00:29:42.920 --> 00:29:44.000
He came to me

00:29:44.160 --> 00:29:44.880
in September

00:29:45.920 --> 00:29:47.310
and brought a stack of cash,

00:29:48.160 --> 00:29:49.440
asking for

00:29:49.750 --> 00:29:50.510
special treatment.

00:29:51.640 --> 00:29:52.920
Of course I said no.

00:29:53.960 --> 00:29:54.880
He got

00:29:55.000 --> 00:29:56.000
really angry

00:29:56.550 --> 00:29:57.350
and said

00:29:58.310 --> 00:29:59.640
he'd do whatever it takes

00:30:00.000 --> 00:30:00.720
to take me down.

00:30:01.880 --> 00:30:02.790
That's why

00:30:03.400 --> 00:30:03.830
I was wary

00:30:03.830 --> 00:30:05.000
when I first met

00:30:05.640 --> 00:30:06.550
Han Bin.

00:30:08.240 --> 00:30:09.640
Maybe I was wrong.

00:30:11.160 --> 00:30:12.070
They're brothers,

00:30:12.640 --> 00:30:13.590
yet not the same.

00:30:17.720 --> 00:30:18.590
September?

00:30:18.920 --> 00:30:19.400
Yeah.

00:30:20.920 --> 00:30:21.640
Around the time

00:30:21.790 --> 00:30:23.110
your mom passed away.

00:30:24.400 --> 00:30:25.070
I met Han Bin

00:30:25.200 --> 00:30:26.790
in September.

00:30:31.750 --> 00:30:33.310
What's with the tantrum?

00:30:33.550 --> 00:30:34.880
This is the best restaurant here.

00:30:35.070 --> 00:30:36.200
Someone must recognize you.

00:30:36.400 --> 00:30:37.640
Our fight's fine.

00:30:37.920 --> 00:30:38.640
But if they think

00:30:38.640 --> 00:30:39.640
your dad and mine...

00:30:43.070 --> 00:30:43.680
Are you insane?

00:30:43.960 --> 00:30:44.680
From the start,

00:30:44.720 --> 00:30:46.000
you had ulterior motives.

00:30:46.310 --> 00:30:47.440
You liar!

00:30:49.350 --> 00:30:50.350
Ulterior motives?

00:30:51.310 --> 00:30:52.550
Dating without purpose

00:30:52.590 --> 00:30:53.110
would hurt

00:30:53.160 --> 00:30:54.440
both sides.

00:30:54.680 --> 00:30:55.400
Think you're

00:30:55.440 --> 00:30:56.110
such a catch?

00:30:56.510 --> 00:30:57.830
Are you the prettiest on campus?

00:30:57.960 --> 00:30:59.310
If not for Meng Siyuan,

00:30:59.400 --> 00:31:00.680
how would I date you?

00:31:02.070 --> 00:31:03.160
Your writing is good,

00:31:03.640 --> 00:31:04.720
but without me, you think

00:31:04.790 --> 00:31:05.880
you'd win that award?

00:31:06.270 --> 00:31:07.200
So naive!

00:31:07.830 --> 00:31:08.550
Honestly,

00:31:09.030 --> 00:31:10.270
"Vanity in the Autumn Wind"

00:31:10.310 --> 00:31:11.200
is too pretentious.

00:31:11.680 --> 00:31:12.590
I read it on the radio

00:31:12.680 --> 00:31:13.830
just to get close to you.

00:31:14.590 --> 00:31:15.510
There's no such thing

00:31:15.550 --> 00:31:16.510
as love at first sight.

00:31:16.640 --> 00:31:17.680
Without money,

00:31:17.750 --> 00:31:19.400
love is doomed!

00:31:28.590 --> 00:31:29.510
We're adults.

00:31:30.160 --> 00:31:30.750
Be realistic.

00:31:31.270 --> 00:31:31.750
My parents

00:31:31.790 --> 00:31:32.920
will ignore your background,

00:31:33.680 --> 00:31:34.510
but you can't meet

00:31:34.590 --> 00:31:36.030
your poor relatives again.

00:31:36.510 --> 00:31:37.200
Win the bid,

00:31:38.110 --> 00:31:38.790
then we marry.

00:31:39.240 --> 00:31:40.590
You'll go from rags

00:31:40.960 --> 00:31:41.920
to riches.

00:31:44.350 --> 00:31:44.880
Stop!

00:31:44.920 --> 00:31:46.350
Liar!

00:31:46.590 --> 00:31:47.110
Bastard!

00:31:47.110 --> 00:31:47.790
Stop it!

00:31:49.350 --> 00:31:50.070
Han Bin,

00:31:51.110 --> 00:31:52.030
listen.

00:31:54.030 --> 00:31:55.110
You have no right

00:31:55.350 --> 00:31:56.680
to talk about love

00:31:57.200 --> 00:31:58.400
and have it.

00:32:01.350 --> 00:32:02.510
I'm good.

00:32:03.110 --> 00:32:04.550
Don't need you to fix me.

00:32:08.680 --> 00:32:09.400
You

00:32:09.960 --> 00:32:11.350
don't deserve me.

00:32:11.720 --> 00:32:12.960
We're done!

00:32:14.750 --> 00:32:15.480
Goodbye!

00:32:38.440 --> 00:32:38.960
Hello?

00:32:40.400 --> 00:32:41.200
Wanzhi!

00:32:42.790 --> 00:32:43.510
Grandma Yu,

00:32:44.200 --> 00:32:45.110
tell my dad

00:32:45.720 --> 00:32:46.440
I was wrong.

00:32:46.920 --> 00:32:47.720
He was right.

00:32:48.960 --> 00:32:50.270
I've bought a train ticket.

00:32:50.960 --> 00:32:51.920
I'm going to school.

00:32:53.200 --> 00:32:53.750
Can't face him.

00:32:55.000 --> 00:32:55.680
Wanzhi?

00:32:58.960 --> 00:32:59.510
Yu,

00:32:59.790 --> 00:33:00.590
what did she say?

00:33:15.720 --> 00:33:17.270
She came all this way

00:33:17.310 --> 00:33:18.480
and didn't even have a meal.

00:33:20.400 --> 00:33:21.270
Mr. Meng,

00:33:21.790 --> 00:33:23.440
shall we go look for her?

00:33:24.400 --> 00:33:25.510
She's grown up.

00:33:26.350 --> 00:33:27.160
There are things

00:33:27.750 --> 00:33:28.720
she'll have to face,

00:33:29.720 --> 00:33:30.550
and some hurdles

00:33:30.720 --> 00:33:32.160
she has to cross alone.

00:33:33.680 --> 00:33:34.920
Let her be.

00:33:48.440 --> 00:33:49.110
Yudan?

00:33:50.070 --> 00:33:50.750
Are you hungry?

00:33:55.880 --> 00:33:57.270
These are offerings for Ms. Fang.

00:33:57.750 --> 00:33:59.440
My mom said they're blessed.

00:34:00.110 --> 00:34:00.960
If you eat them,

00:34:01.200 --> 00:34:02.110
Ms. Fang will be happy.

00:34:02.880 --> 00:34:04.640
You came to visit her grave?

00:34:10.280 --> 00:34:11.000
Thanks.

00:34:11.590 --> 00:34:12.280
As it should be.

00:34:16.320 --> 00:34:16.800
Wanzhi,

00:34:18.030 --> 00:34:20.150
uh... are you on the train?

00:34:21.000 --> 00:34:22.480
Why didn't Han Bin drive you back?

00:34:24.230 --> 00:34:25.000
Don't mention him.

00:34:27.590 --> 00:34:28.920
I didn't let you down this time.

00:34:29.760 --> 00:34:30.760
I said bye first.

00:34:39.360 --> 00:34:39.960
Yudan,

00:34:41.150 --> 00:34:42.760
let's study hard.

00:34:43.190 --> 00:34:44.710
My mom wanted me to go to grad school.

00:34:45.760 --> 00:34:46.840
You do better in school.

00:34:47.670 --> 00:34:48.550
Take the exam with me.

00:34:51.510 --> 00:34:52.030
Okay.

00:35:11.840 --> 00:35:13.070
Next!

00:35:14.150 --> 00:35:14.800
Which one?

00:35:23.480 --> 00:35:24.920
The chef must be happy.

00:35:24.960 --> 00:35:25.960
She gave you so much.

00:35:26.440 --> 00:35:27.150
In your dreams.

00:35:27.190 --> 00:35:28.070
Two servings,

00:35:28.230 --> 00:35:29.150
but just one bowl.

00:35:29.150 --> 00:35:29.800
Let's share it.

00:35:29.960 --> 00:35:30.400
Here.

00:35:38.670 --> 00:35:39.360
Fang Wanzhi.

00:35:43.960 --> 00:35:44.590
You're...?

00:35:48.320 --> 00:35:49.280
What are you doing?

00:35:50.360 --> 00:35:51.590
I'm giving her a lesson.

00:35:51.840 --> 00:35:52.710
Stay out of it.

00:35:54.510 --> 00:35:55.630
Who do you think you are?

00:35:56.760 --> 00:35:58.360
You, a poor village girl, are pretending

00:35:58.480 --> 00:35:59.550
to be an official's kid

00:35:59.630 --> 00:36:00.840
and stealing my boyfriend.

00:36:01.550 --> 00:36:02.550
Have you no shame?

00:36:04.000 --> 00:36:04.840
Your boyfriend?

00:36:05.030 --> 00:36:06.510
Han Bin is my boyfriend.

00:36:06.710 --> 00:36:08.030
We grew up together

00:36:08.070 --> 00:36:09.190
and have been together for years.

00:36:09.550 --> 00:36:10.320
Aren't you ashamed

00:36:10.440 --> 00:36:11.590
of being the other woman?

00:36:13.150 --> 00:36:14.280
Fang Wanzhi

00:36:15.480 --> 00:36:16.960
is posing as the vice mayor's kid

00:36:17.150 --> 00:36:18.480
and cashing in on it.

00:36:18.760 --> 00:36:20.110
She even pursued my boyfriend!

00:36:20.360 --> 00:36:21.360
Remember her face.

00:36:22.070 --> 00:36:22.920
Don't be fooled.

00:36:23.960 --> 00:36:24.510
Look at...

00:36:32.670 --> 00:36:33.070
Wen,

00:36:33.280 --> 00:36:33.920
are you alright?

00:36:35.920 --> 00:36:36.710
Fang Wanzhi!

00:36:37.150 --> 00:36:38.190
You're dead!

00:36:47.800 --> 00:36:48.510
Fang Wanzhi!

00:36:48.960 --> 00:36:49.510
You can't go.

00:36:49.800 --> 00:36:50.670
Apologize to her!

00:36:53.590 --> 00:36:54.230
Wanzhi.

00:36:55.070 --> 00:36:56.710
Wanzhi, are you okay?

00:36:59.800 --> 00:37:00.510
Han Bin, you...

00:37:24.230 --> 00:37:24.760
Come on!

00:37:25.150 --> 00:37:25.960
- Fight me!
- Run!

00:37:26.070 --> 00:37:26.510
Come on!

00:37:26.920 --> 00:37:27.510
Run!

00:37:44.840 --> 00:37:46.000
This is your statement.

00:37:46.360 --> 00:37:46.920
Check it.

00:37:47.150 --> 00:37:48.230
If everything's correct,

00:37:48.510 --> 00:37:49.190
write here:

00:37:49.190 --> 00:37:50.280
I've read this.

00:37:50.760 --> 00:37:51.630
It's correct.

00:38:01.230 --> 00:38:02.230
I wanna see my sister,

00:38:02.920 --> 00:38:03.800
Fang Wanzhi.

00:38:05.710 --> 00:38:06.510
No way.

00:38:06.880 --> 00:38:07.840
By law,

00:38:08.000 --> 00:38:09.360
you will be sent

00:38:10.150 --> 00:38:11.480
to lockup.

00:38:14.960 --> 00:38:16.000
You're a Fang.

00:38:16.360 --> 00:38:17.190
He's a Li.

00:38:17.800 --> 00:38:19.070
And you two are not relatives.

00:38:20.030 --> 00:38:21.150
He's my brother anyway.

00:38:22.360 --> 00:38:23.510
I want to see him.

00:38:24.070 --> 00:38:25.150
This is a criminal case.

00:38:25.510 --> 00:38:26.280
Get a lawyer

00:38:26.630 --> 00:38:27.360
if you wanna see him.

00:38:28.800 --> 00:38:30.110
Will he be sentenced?

00:38:34.440 --> 00:38:35.480
How long will he get?

00:38:36.360 --> 00:38:38.190
That depends on the court.

00:38:39.150 --> 00:38:39.630
The key

00:38:39.920 --> 00:38:41.360
is the victim's injuries.

00:38:56.920 --> 00:38:57.760
Fang Wanzhi,

00:38:58.440 --> 00:38:59.280
you're finally here.

00:39:00.230 --> 00:39:00.760
This is

00:39:01.320 --> 00:39:02.320
Han Bin's older brother.

00:39:04.920 --> 00:39:05.510
Mr. Han.

00:39:09.670 --> 00:39:10.630
Fang Wanzhi,

00:39:11.760 --> 00:39:13.280
while you're dating my brother,

00:39:14.320 --> 00:39:14.760
you've got

00:39:14.760 --> 00:39:15.880
another guy.

00:39:16.360 --> 00:39:17.800
Playing both sides?

00:39:18.320 --> 00:39:19.360
Pretty modern of you.

00:39:20.280 --> 00:39:20.670
No.

00:39:20.710 --> 00:39:22.000
Han Bin is in a coma now.

00:39:22.190 --> 00:39:23.480
If he doesn't make it,

00:39:24.960 --> 00:39:27.070
that's intentional homicide.

00:39:27.880 --> 00:39:28.880
Li Xingke

00:39:29.400 --> 00:39:30.550
will be executed.

00:39:31.920 --> 00:39:33.360
You had better

00:39:33.440 --> 00:39:34.280
think long and hard

00:39:34.400 --> 00:39:35.440
about how to handle her.

00:39:36.590 --> 00:39:37.550
If you screw this up,

00:39:39.320 --> 00:39:40.630
my dad won't let it slide.

00:39:41.510 --> 00:39:43.000
Got it.

00:39:48.760 --> 00:39:49.760
Fang Wanzhi!

00:39:50.230 --> 00:39:51.440
How could you do this?

00:39:51.710 --> 00:39:53.230
Pouring soup on someone's head?

00:39:54.150 --> 00:39:55.710
Something this violent

00:39:56.070 --> 00:39:56.510
has never

00:39:56.510 --> 00:39:57.630
happened at our school.

00:39:58.280 --> 00:39:59.440
Make my life easier, okay?

00:39:59.510 --> 00:40:00.110
Mr. Chen,

00:40:00.510 --> 00:40:01.630
calm down.

00:40:02.880 --> 00:40:03.590
Fang Wanzhi,

00:40:04.440 --> 00:40:05.760
the school's budget is tight.

00:40:06.190 --> 00:40:07.510
We've already covered quite a bit.

00:40:08.440 --> 00:40:09.280
The hospital bill

00:40:10.030 --> 00:40:10.760
is on you.

00:40:21.150 --> 00:40:22.920
This passbook is from another county.

00:40:23.110 --> 00:40:24.110
I checked with the bank.

00:40:24.150 --> 00:40:25.480
They said I can withdraw it here.

00:40:26.150 --> 00:40:26.760
Yes.

00:40:27.030 --> 00:40:28.480
But it's a fixed deposit.

00:40:28.630 --> 00:40:30.070
You'll lose a lot of interest.

00:40:30.440 --> 00:40:30.960
I know.

00:40:31.190 --> 00:40:32.190
Please cash it.

00:40:36.400 --> 00:40:37.190
Another withdrawal?

00:40:38.070 --> 00:40:39.630
What's going on at home?

00:40:39.800 --> 00:40:40.630
Third time

00:40:40.710 --> 00:40:41.800
in two weeks.

00:40:43.070 --> 00:40:44.360
Hate to see you

00:40:44.510 --> 00:40:45.710
lose all that interest.

00:40:49.480 --> 00:40:50.510
The bill's paid?

00:40:51.150 --> 00:40:52.510
Yeah, 10,000 yuan.

00:40:52.920 --> 00:40:53.670
Who paid it?

00:40:54.480 --> 00:40:55.230
She hasn't left.

00:40:55.880 --> 00:40:56.590
Right over there.

00:41:05.280 --> 00:41:05.960
Mrs. Li.

00:41:08.360 --> 00:41:08.960
Wanzhi,

00:41:09.800 --> 00:41:10.590
you're here.

00:41:16.230 --> 00:41:17.320
Sorry.

00:41:19.320 --> 00:41:20.030
It's fine.

00:41:22.110 --> 00:41:22.840
Really sorry.

00:41:24.510 --> 00:41:25.760
Good girl, don't cry.

00:41:26.510 --> 00:41:27.280
Don't cry.

00:41:27.480 --> 00:41:28.510
Sorry.

00:41:33.110 --> 00:41:34.550
I'm sorry, Mrs. Li.

00:41:34.670 --> 00:41:35.550
It's okay.

00:41:41.920 --> 00:41:42.480
Mrs. Li.

00:41:45.030 --> 00:41:46.000
What are you doing?

00:41:46.510 --> 00:41:47.630
You paid the hospital fees.

00:41:50.590 --> 00:41:51.710
My son hurt someone.

00:41:51.920 --> 00:41:52.480
The bill

00:41:52.510 --> 00:41:53.630
should be on me.

00:41:54.630 --> 00:41:55.320
I know

00:41:55.670 --> 00:41:57.590
you've already paid tens of thousands.

00:41:58.590 --> 00:41:59.760
I'll pay you back.

00:42:02.190 --> 00:42:03.480
Yudan did that for me.

00:42:04.070 --> 00:42:04.840
That's just him.

00:42:06.360 --> 00:42:07.480
That little toad.

00:42:08.030 --> 00:42:08.590
He really went

00:42:08.590 --> 00:42:09.670
and fought for you.

00:42:15.550 --> 00:42:16.960
Well, I always joked

00:42:16.960 --> 00:42:17.360
he was...

00:42:18.440 --> 00:42:18.960
a toad

00:42:18.960 --> 00:42:20.190
dreaming of swan meat.

00:42:20.670 --> 00:42:21.670
You misunderstood.

00:42:22.110 --> 00:42:23.030
I'm his sister.

00:42:24.670 --> 00:42:25.550
I know.

00:42:27.960 --> 00:42:28.840
When you were kids,

00:42:29.440 --> 00:42:30.710
he did see you as a sister.

00:42:31.480 --> 00:42:33.110
But things change when you grow up.

00:42:34.000 --> 00:42:35.230
With his scores,

00:42:36.030 --> 00:42:37.670
he could've gone to
any school in Beijing.

00:42:38.320 --> 00:42:39.960
Yet he chose your school instead.

